Cell["\<\
For the case of H applied along y we obtain (under the assumption that the z \
driving field cannot cause an inductance:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7830782860733256`*^9, 3.7830782964727197`*^9}, {
  3.783078390230366*^9, 
  3.783078404627368*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"87f80a31-ed50-4dee-b87e-\
