Cell["\<\
We now need to consider the forward SOT due to charge currents in the NM \
layer (as discussed in Berger paper, section 3), which will increase all \
inductances by a factor of two.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.78387394934767*^9, 3.7838739880348835`*^9}, {
  3.783874180516124*^9, 3.7838741891318455`*^9}, {3.7838742286715536`*^9, 
  3.7838742544728003`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"608a512c-f281-4b35-9be8-\
fbcf55f88ad8"],

Cell["The final expressions for LNM are thus", "Text",
